  "text": "Integrin a7 is linked to chromosome 12q13. The disease has been reported in 4 isolated patients without apparent gender preference [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . The children were the products of nonconsanguineous parents. Mutations included deletions, splice-site mutations, and heterozygous missense mutations.",
